      <title>民意调查的平静让印度期权交易者面临意外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/calm-over-polls-leaves-india-option-traders-exposed-to-surprises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度期权交易员似乎相对不担心即将到来的大选将扰乱市场的稳步走高，从而可能使他们容易受到意外结果的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/calm-over-polls-leaves-india-option-traders-exposed-to-surprises</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 01:35:02 GMT</pubDate>
